staxel.village.character.dialogue.Emilia: (안함)You know I can't bake for you every day regardless how many times you ask!
(안함)I do hope my family doesn't decide to visit the island again...
(안함)Next time there would probably be a lot more pomp...
(안함)It's hard being royal... I'm glad I don't have to deal with it any more!
(안함)You'd never be able to get me to go back!
